title: Hubble captures birth of giant storm on Neptune

title_detail.value: Hubble captures birth of giant storm on Neptune

summary: Images taken by the Hubble Space Telescope document the formation of a Great Dark Spot on Neptune for the first time, report researchers in a new study.
